---
import CTA from "../CTA.astro";
import ServiceCard from "../ServiceCard.astro";
---

<div
    class="flex flex-col text-white gap-8 bg-zinc-800 py-16 2xl:py-32 px-small-padding md:px-medium-padding 2xl:px-large-padding"
>
    <h1 class="text-4xl 2xl:text-6xl font-semibold">Services</h1>
	<p class="text-md sm:text-xl">We focus on real-life safety concerns that families worry about every day — and address them with simple, reliable solutions that don’t overwhelm.</p>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col 2xl:flex-wrap gap-16 items-center 2xl:items-stretch text-white"
    >
        <ServiceCard
            title="Fall Prevention & Nighttime Safety"
            image="fall.svg"
            description=`Falls are one of the most common risks for seniors, especially at night. We install automatic, motion‑activated lighting in key areas like hallways and bathrooms so your loved one can move safely without fumbling for switches in the dark.`
            link=""
        />
        <ServiceCard
            title="Emergency Help — Made Simple"
            image="help.svg"
            description=`In an emergency, every second matters. We set up hands‑free emergency calling that works by voice alone, so help is always accessible — even if a phone isn’t nearby or a wearable device isn’t being used.`
            link=""
        />
        <ServiceCard
            title="Awareness & Peace of Mind for Families"
            image="bell.svg"
            description=`For families who can’t be there all the time, knowing what’s happening day to day brings peace of mind. We offer gentle activity and door alerts that notify you of unusual patterns — without invading privacy or creating constant interruptions.`
            link=""
        />
        <ServiceCard
            title="Reliable Setup & Connectivity"
            image="wifi.svg"
            description=`Safety technology only works if it’s dependable. We make sure Wi‑Fi coverage is strong where it matters most and keep systems simple, stable, and easy to use — with no confusing apps or unnecessary complexity.`
            link=""
        />
    </div>
    <CTA text="Contact Us" destination="/contact" />
</div>
